Your software calculator construction kit

This is construction kit for you to create your own wonderful calculator, for every different purpose like hexiadecimal, duodecimal calculation, counting score of game.

This kit contains basic architecture of calculator with simple calculation engine and its UI as basic sample, which you can freely customize for your purpose!

Programmed in scala, and the sample is in Java for Android.
You can just replace development environment for your final target, like web application; it is designed to be easy to bring calculator body, just fit to your UI.
You would also want to customize your calculation, you can simply add your functions to calculation engine.
